        <img src="~/Images/home/scene.jpg" class="img-rounded" />
        <h3>Beautiful Scenary</h3>
        <p>Click the following button to open up a new tab in the browser for checking the codes of the Master Page designed by us.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-4">
        <img src="~/Images/home/well.jpg" class="img-rounded" />
        <h3>About Us</h3>
